description:
Evolution - The Creation of our Earth | Nature Documentary

Watch 'Earth - Our Precious & Endangered Home' here: https://youtu.be/hwWhyHilu8g

It started in the water. It came ashore. It conquered our planet. The origin of life is probably the most fascinating story our earth has to tell.
Come with us on our journey through the impressive fauna of our earth. Explore the beautiful, colorful world of coral reefs. Marvel at the diverse life in Africa, Australia and South America. Experience incredible strategies for adapting to a wide variety of habitats.

Overwhelming shots, exciting and rare insights into hidden worlds.

▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬

▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬

Free Documentary is dedicated to bring high-class documentaries to you on youtube for free. With the latest camera equipment used by well-known filmmakers working for famous production studios. You will see fascinating shots from the deep seas and up in the air, capturing great stories and pictures from everything our beautiful and interesting planet has to offer. 

Enjoy stories about nature, wildlife, culture, people, history and more to come.
